News from our newspaper (Reporter Yang Zhaokui) The "China Shared Accommodation Development Report 2020" (hereinafter referred to as the "Report") recently released by the National Information Center Sharing Economy Research Center shows that due to the impact of the epidemic, in the first five months of 2020, the transaction volume of my country's shared accommodation market fell by 72.1% year-on-year.
