Chinanews.com, Xiamen, July 26 (Yang Fushan Zhang Shushan Xu Jingyi) The Vascular Surgery Department of Shanghai Changhai Hospital, Naval Military Medical University, a well-known vascular surgery center in China, signed a contract with the Vascular Surgery Department of Zhongshan Hospital Affiliated to Xiamen University on the 25th to establish a collaboration center to promote exchanges and cooperation between the two sides in the field of vascular surgery, especially in the field of acute and severe aortic diseases.
